    <title>博客更新日志</title>
    <link href="/2021/04/10/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97/"/>
    <url>/2021/04/10/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="博客可能相关内容"><a href="#博客可能相关内容" class="headerlink" title="博客可能相关内容"></a>博客可能相关内容</h1><p>1.学习过程中解决的一些问题</p><p>2.生活记录向</p><p>3.乱七八糟的想法</p><h1 id="更新记录如下"><a href="#更新记录如下" class="headerlink" title="更新记录如下"></a>更新记录如下</h1><h2 id="2021-04-12"><a href="#2021-04-12" class="headerlink" title="2021/04/12"></a>2021/04/12</h2><h3 id="修改主页标题并增加了个性签名"><a href="#修改主页标题并增加了个性签名" class="headerlink" title="修改主页标题并增加了个性签名"></a>修改主页标题并增加了个性签名</h3><p>全局配置文件中的_config.yml的site部分</p><h3 id="配置sitemap"><a href="#配置sitemap" class="headerlink" title="配置sitemap"></a>配置sitemap</h3><p>下载了<br>npm install hexo-generator-sitemap –save</p><p>修改了全局配置文件_config.yml中</p><p>增加了</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript">sitemap:<br>    path: sitemap.xml<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="增加不蒜子统计"><a href="#增加不蒜子统计" class="headerlink" title="增加不蒜子统计"></a>增加不蒜子统计</h3><p>详见<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_43935907/article/details/89332997">https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_43935907/article/details/89332997</a></p><p>yilia出问题了，重装了一遍</p><h3 id="增加版权信息"><a href="#增加版权信息" class="headerlink" title="增加版权信息"></a>增加版权信息</h3><p>详见<a href="https://blog.zscself.com/posts/ee4d9ecb/">https://blog.zscself.com/posts/ee4d9ecb/</a></p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="2021-04-11"><a href="#2021-04-11" class="headerlink" title="2021/04/11"></a>2021/04/11</h2><h3 id="增加了文章”Arduino中LOOP如何实现循环执行“"><a href="#增加了文章”Arduino中LOOP如何实现循环执行“" class="headerlink" title="增加了文章”Arduino中LOOP如何实现循环执行“"></a>增加了文章”Arduino中LOOP如何实现循环执行“</h3><h3 id="增加了文章阅读次数显示"><a href="#增加了文章阅读次数显示" class="headerlink" title="增加了文章阅读次数显示"></a>增加了文章阅读次数显示</h3><p>修改了BLOG\themes\yilia\layout\_partial下article.ejs文件中内容</p><p>在</p><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript">&lt;%# 注释掉-partial(&#x27;post/title&#x27;, &#123;class_name: &#x27;article-title&#x27;&#125;) %&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>后增加了</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript">&lt;!--显示阅读次数--&gt;<br>        &lt;% <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!index &amp;&amp; post.comments)&#123; %&gt;<br>          &lt;br/&gt;<br>          &lt;a <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;cloud-tie-join-count&quot;</span> href=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;javascript:void(0);&quot;</span>   style=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;color:gray;font-size:14px;&quot;</span>&gt;<br>          &lt;span <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span></span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;icon-sort&quot;</span>&gt;&lt;/span&gt;<br>          &lt;span id=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;busuanzi_container_page_pv&quot;</span> style=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;color:#ef7522;font-size:14px;&quot;</span>&gt;<br>          阅读数: <span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">span</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;busuanzi_value_page_pv&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">span</span>&gt;</span></span>次 &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;<br>          &lt;/span&gt;<br>          &lt;/a&gt;<br>&lt;% &#125; %&gt;<br>&lt;!--显示阅读次数完毕--&gt;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2021-04-10"><a href="#2021-04-10" class="headerlink" title="2021/04/10"></a>2021/04/10</h2><h3 id="增加了文章“博客更新日志”"><a href="#增加了文章“博客更新日志”" class="headerlink" title="增加了文章“博客更新日志”"></a>增加了文章“博客更新日志”</h3><h3 id="增加了文章“关于西西弗斯的思考”"><a href="#增加了文章“关于西西弗斯的思考”" class="headerlink" title="增加了文章“关于西西弗斯的思考”"></a>增加了文章“关于西西弗斯的思考”</h3><h3 id="增加了置顶功能"><a href="#增加了置顶功能" class="headerlink" title="增加了置顶功能"></a>增加了置顶功能</h3><p>修改了BLOG\node_modules\hexo-generator-index\lib\generator.js中的内容</p><p>原为</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript"><span class="hljs-meta">&#x27;use strict&#x27;</span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> pagination = <span class="hljs-built_in">require</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;hexo-pagination&#x27;</span>);<br><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> &#123; sort &#125; = <span class="hljs-built_in">require</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;timsort&#x27;</span>);<br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">module</span>.exports = <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span>(<span class="hljs-params">locals</span>) </span>&#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> config = <span class="hljs-built_in">this</span>.config;<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> posts = locals.posts.sort(config.index_generator.order_by);<br><br>  sort(posts.data, <span class="hljs-function">(<span class="hljs-params">a, b</span>) =&gt;</span> (b.sticky || <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) - (a.sticky || <span class="hljs-number">0</span>));<br><br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> paginationDir = config.pagination_dir || <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;page&#x27;</span>;<br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> path = config.index_generator.path || <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>;<br><br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> pagination(path, posts, &#123;<br>    perPage: config.index_generator.per_page,<br>    layout: [<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;index&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;archive&#x27;</span>],<br>    format: paginationDir + <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;/%d/&#x27;</span>,<br>    data: &#123;<br>      __index: <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br>    &#125;<br>  &#125;);<br>&#125;;<br><br><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改后为</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><